               <code code="43685-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="WARNINGS AND PRECAUTIONS SECTION"/>
               <title>GENERAL WARNINGS AND PRECAUTIONS</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>WARNING: Administration of nitrogen may be hazardous or contraindicated.  For<br/>use only by or under the supervision of a licensed practitioner who is<br/>experienced in the use and administration of nitrogen and is familiar<br/>with the indications, effects, dosages, methods, and frequency and<br/>duration of administration and with hazards, contraindications, and<br/>side effects and the precautions to be taken.  Rx Only</paragraph>
               </text>
